      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "KEY QUESTION — Of total AI-data-center capex, how much goes to POWER GENERATION (the gensets / turbines / fuel cells Weichai sells)?\nSHORT ANSWER — A small share of total AIDC capex (IT / GPUs dominate), but the LARGEST growth area within facility spend — and Weichai sits in the fastest-growing \nslice: onsite PRIMARY power.",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "AA4XtgyHdWbx9E6YqZape",
      "originalText": "KEY QUESTION — Of total AI-data-center capex, how much goes to POWER GENERATION (the gensets / turbines / fuel cells Weichai sells)?\nSHORT ANSWER — A small share of total AIDC capex (IT / GPUs dominate), but the LARGEST growth area within facility spend — and Weichai sits in the fastest-growing slice: onsite PRIMARY power.",
