      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "KEY DIVERGENCE — The US onsite-PRIMARY-power boom (gas engines, SOFC) is the largest & fastest-growing power-gen TAM, but it is an EXPORT play for Weichai into the \nmost competitive / political market. China (Weichai's stronghold) is mainly a BACKUP-genset market — and already EXPORTS gensets into the global build-out (SCMP).",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "shT-T0xq8P87jwyZi2ldl",
      "originalText": "KEY DIVERGENCE — The US onsite-PRIMARY-power boom (gas engines, SOFC) is the largest & fastest-growing power-gen TAM, but it is an EXPORT play for Weichai into the most competitive / political market. China (Weichai's stronghold) is mainly a BACKUP-genset market — and already EXPORTS gensets into the global build-out (SCMP).",
