      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "IMPLICATION FOR THE THESIS",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "cWw-vRaj_UbZUBt9jUVsJ",
      "originalText": "IMPLICATION FOR THE THESIS",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 18
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 484429553,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "648oeIfpM8xhdNPqIrIRJ",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 99.74026489257812,
      "y": 1644,
      "strokeColor": "#0ca678",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 850.5194702148438,
      "height": 50,
      "seed": 2088991871,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782462333239,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "①  Power generation = a small % of total AIDC capex, BUT a fast-growing, supply-\nconstrained niche.",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "lyU1T8_7g8wnJ3wer5f-W",
      "originalText": "①  Power generation = a small % of total AIDC capex, BUT a fast-growing, supply-constrained niche.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 43
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 181061841,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "czn8Ck3Bk8PXlI4-ZGBNL",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1036.4019775390625,
      "y": 1631.5,
      "strokeColor": "#0ca678",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 797.196044921875,
      "height": 75,
      "seed": 2096993439,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782462333240,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "②  Weichai TAM ≠ just the ~$14bn backup market — it's the expanding onsite \nPRIMARY-power market (33 GW BTM, 8–10 GW turbines, plus engine / fuel-cell \noverflow).",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "5InKE1LR6GXKzHY0tdRJt",
      "originalText": "②  Weichai TAM ≠ just the ~$14bn backup market — it's the expanding onsite PRIMARY-power market (33 GW BTM, 8–10 GW turbines, plus engine / fuel-cell overflow).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 68
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1492879025,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "FGy96LK55DFEwVjueo0th",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 108.51028442382812,
      "y": 1740,
      "strokeColor": "#0ca678",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 832.9794311523438,
      "height": 50,
      "seed": 1925163199,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782462333240,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "③  Bull case: the category EXPANDS (structural grid crunch) AND Weichai TAKES \nSHARE (diesel 15–16% → 30% target; gas / SOFC ramp).",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Ojl5-j_nAhkXWgIbc6BgN",
      "originalText": "③  Bull case: the category EXPANDS (structural grid crunch) AND Weichai TAKES SHARE (diesel 15–16% → 30% target; gas / SOFC ramp).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 43
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 35227793,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "MdGedy9h_8QKzk3JFA3P8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1001.8902587890625,
      "y": 1740,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 866.219482421875,
      "height": 50,
      "seed": 1802123487,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782462333240,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "④  Watch: how the ~33 GW BTM splits — turbines (GE Vernova / Siemens / MHI) vs \nrecip engines (Weichai / Cummins / INNIO / CAT) vs fuel cells (Bloom / Weichai SOFC).",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "97WQINcN08cPW2-jqZ-do",
      "originalText": "④  Watch: how the ~33 GW BTM splits — turbines (GE Vernova / Siemens / MHI) vs recip engines (Weichai / Cummins / INNIO / CAT) vs fuel cells (Bloom / Weichai SOFC).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 43
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1974127903,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "TJuxjeoUxM3hb7juWvnN3",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 87.99066162109375,
      "y": 1833,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1784.0186767578125,
      "height": 75,
      "seed": 1821230335,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782462333241,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Sources: CreditSights / Futurum / Goldman / IEEE (hyperscaler capex); Epoch AI / Thunder Said Energy / alpha-matica (capex breakdown); construction-cost guides (electrical \n40–45%, $/MW); SemiAnalysis / S&P / Latitude / Jefferies (US onsite / BTM); DCD / SCMP / Fortune Business Insights (China). 2025–26 · estimates — verify before modeling.\n         ·          Converted from Obsidian note 'AIDC Capex Landscape' (Weichai Power · 2338 HK).",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wzn3F2ihdwHFDCEz0EkzT",
      "originalText": "Sources: CreditSights / Futurum / Goldman / IEEE (hyperscaler capex); Epoch AI / Thunder Said Energy / alpha-matica (capex breakdown); construction-cost guides (electrical 40–45%, $/MW); SemiAnalysis / S&P / Latitude / Jefferies (US onsite / BTM); DCD / SCMP / Fortune Business Insights (China). 2025–26 · estimates — verify before modeling.          ·          Converted from Obsidian note 'AIDC Capex Landscape' (Weichai Power · 2338 HK).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 68
    },
